<DOCNO> AP900522-0012 </DOCNO>
<TEXT>
the last newhart aired monday night the 
184th episode of the longrunning cbs situation comedy and it 
closed with a surprise ending of sorts 
as innkeeper dick loudon comedian bob newhart presided over the 
stratford inn for eight seasons a frustrated pillar of reason 
among various rustics zanies and spoiled yuppie brats afflicting 
the town of stratford vt 
in mondays episode the townspeople sold their town lock 
stock and barrel to a japanese businessman who erects the 
luxurious 5000room tagadachiville hotel dick is the only 
