in most computers no matter how powerful computation proceeds 
as one calculation at a time known as serial processing 
in some problems multiple results might be calculable 
independently of each other and a parallel processing machine 
is designed to save time by doing those independent calculations 
simultaneously 
us and west german scientists have developed some parallel 
processing computers and some very specialized machines are 
available 
