fill the companies she contacted all asked her if she was renting 
the limousine for a prom they then told her she must rent it for 
at least six hours and pay the lump sum up front 
i asked them why it was different for a prom and i never 
could get a straight answer she said 
during prom time thats the way all the companies do it 
