cause large kills of dolphins porpoise northern fur seals and 
seabirds the fleets also intercept north american salmon and 
threaten the viability of albacore tuna and red flying squid 
stocks he said 
the driftnet provisions would provide new leverage to gain a 
global ban on this destructive fishing technology which is 
threatening ocean environment reichman said 
the measure establishes a congressional goal of gaining a global 
moratorium on high seas driftnet fishing through a resolution the 
united nations general assembly approved in december that 
resolution calls for the moratorium on largescale driftnet 
fishing to go into effect next year 
