admitted in the house of commons that the future of the meech lake 
accord is in serious doubt 
the proposed constitutional amendment would give all 10 
provinces special powers and recognize quebec as a distinct 
society within canada by law all 10 provinces must ratify meech 
by june 23 or the proposal will expire 
bouchard the former environment minister opposes any change to 
the 1987 accord recommendations for change are now before the 
government 
