in a separate case is mentally defective only if she is unable to 
understand that others may not have sex with her without her 
consent 
tate said the investigation was continuing but declined to 
elaborate 
defense lawyers say the girl was intelligent enough to have said 
no 
but the grand jury found that mg was one whom kevin 
scherzer and kyle scherzer and peter quigley and richard corcoran 
jr knew or should have known was physically helpless mentally 
defective or mentally incapacitated 
