its bad but it wasnt worse than what i expected he said 
what is worse than i expected is the willingness of the people to 
accept criminal activity id like to push down those 
expectations 
greenberg himself is somewhat unexpected black balding the 
grandson of a russian jew who emigrated to houston and married a 
black woman the family shortened its name to green and were 
practicing methodists but greenberg changed his name back again 
