the public safety commissioner opened police stations inside the 
projects and started chasing drug dealers on scooters 
youll see crime being reduced dramatically in the areas in 
which we control greenberg predicted eventually that will be 
the city as a whole i would want to see it for a sixmonth period 
i wouldnt want to see a month or two months thats 
flashinthepan 
even after a year i wouldnt be satisified until you really 
turn the corner youre going to have two or three years of 
decreasing crime in areas that youre impacting you better hope 
its not increasing in the areas youre not impacting 
part of greenbergs crimefighting strategy is to convince 
